:42:31.000Z","msg":"由20小辣開始日日食，好快食大辣都冇難度啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e8842d56cf4d5e50339f2f5bdcc48ce5d9aa96","tid":2068802,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:15:13.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"268294665513e79ba0980f32c540853a123fb677","tid":2068802,"uid":153615,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T18:55:01.000Z","msg":"香港就係有呢啲仆街搞到大部份餐廳啲應該要辣嘅嘢食完全唔辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed43e61fa7a19563aeae7e42c458aa6146fd6b5","tid":2068802,"uid":345781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T19:03:41.000Z","msg":"我都好鍾意食辣，食到大辣米線。<br />\n不過次次食完第日就會肚痛，柯到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痛。"},{"pid":"c40b14388675cd998c8e43528fece1d18775f8f3","tid":2068802,"uid":2716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T15:36:52.000Z","msg":"起碼你哋係驚肚痾所以唔食<br />\n我係連少少辣都食唔到<br />\n我都覺得辣好香<br />\n但譚仔食10小辣都食到流晒鼻水"},{"pid":"d8d6e06f5419369454c63b990e80219a4c05bed9","tid":2068802,"uid":42430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96be913523726abd3b87706059e1c6d8f9d410d8","tid":2068802,"uid":346854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:07:36.000Z","msg":"食撚完第二日個肚好撚痛 屙屎嗰陣屎眼又熱到仆街 但又好鍾意食辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T16:36:22.000Z","msg":"食前食後飲奶打底"},{"pid":"678a90bdade6b6cea38dd949920ce3fd5490b813","tid":2068802,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c40b14388675cd998c8e43528fece1d18775f8f3","tid":2068802,"uid":2716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T15:36:52.000Z","msg":"起碼你哋係驚肚痾所以唔食<br />\n我係連少少辣都食唔到<br />\n我都覺得辣好香<br />\n但譚仔食10小辣都食到流晒鼻水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T00:13:49.000Z","msg":"譚仔辣但唔香"},{"pid":"a7b5c7549e